title: Aagaasa Veedu Kattum Lyrics Tamil (Dear Comrade)
stanzas:
aagaasa veedu kattum
un kannile
chinoondu koodukatta
vandhen.

sangeetha pathangalin
perosaiyil sokki
unnodu vaasal varai
vandhen.

men aambal punnaigaiyin
peranbile
vinmeenil veededuppen
indre

unnai kaanave ye..
aasai ovvondrum
otrai kaalil nindrengum
adharkkaagave ye..
vaasal padiyoram
endhan vazhkai kudiyerum

evarum kaangala
ivan padum avadhi
idhayath thudippil
alaigalin surudhi

vizhigal malarvathai
rasithida virumbi
urakkam poividum
veettukku thirumbi

aagaasa veedu kattum
un kannile..
sangeetha pathangalin
perosaiyil sokki
..
